## Source Code - GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 (AGPL-3.0-only)

All source code, including but not limited to:

- `crates/` - Compiler and interpreter implementation (Rust)
  - `zymbol-cli/` - Command-line interface
  - `zymbol-lexer/` - Lexical analyzer
  - `zymbol-parser/` - Recursive descent parser
  - `zymbol-ast/` - Abstract syntax tree definitions
  - `zymbol-semantic/` - Semantic analysis and type checking
  - `zymbol-interpreter/` - Tree-walker interpreter runtime
  - `zymbol-compiler/` - AST-to-bytecode compiler
  - `zymbol-bytecode/` - Bytecode instructions and compiled program format
  - `zymbol-vm/` - Register-based virtual machine executor
  - `zymbol-analyzer/` - LSP analysis engine
  - `zymbol-lsp/` - Language Server Protocol implementation
  - `zymbol-formatter/` - Code formatter
  - `zymbol-repl/` - Interactive REPL
  - `zymbol-standalone/` - Standalone executable builder
  - `zymbol-span/` - Source position tracking
  - `zymbol-error/` - Error reporting and diagnostics
  - `zymbol-common/` - Shared types and utilities

**is licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License version 3.0 (AGPL-3.0-only).**

